      "asbval:note": "Cardinal is confirmed as a preprocessing tool and its output can be imported into mass2adduct. However, the specific function 'cardinal2msimat()' is not mentioned in the passages; the paper only states that imzML format (which Cardinal outputs) can be imported via Cardinal. The conversion function name cannot be verified.",
